ry<\/b>: Skorzystaj z narz\u0119dzi i zasob\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re Amazon oferuje w ramach Brand Registry, aby skutecznie reagowa\u0107 na incydenty hijackingu.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, dbanie o zabezpieczenie swojej marki na Amazonie jest niezb\u0119dne, aby zminimalizowa\u0107 ryzyko hijackingu i utrzyma\u0107 morale w zespole. Wdra\u017caj\u0105c powy\u017csze kroki, zwi\u0119kszysz ochron\u0119 swoich produkt\u00f3w oraz reputacj\u0119 marki.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak chroni\u0107 swoj\u0105 mark\u0119 na Amazonie przed hijackowaniem?<\/h1>\n<p>Czy obawiasz si\u0119, \u017ce Twoje pro<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5394,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5393","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5393"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5393"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5393\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5394"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5393"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5393"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp